data.description: This 2 -Story, 2 bedroom, 1.5 bath condo located in Gender Park is ready for it's new owners! Convenience to easy living is right here just seconds from shops, groceries, 33/270 access straight to downtown! Enjoy the community fitness center, pool and common grounds too! New flooring, open kitchen to conversation to living room, half bath on first level with laundry room and garage access! Upstairs you'll find 2 spacious bedrooms w/ walk through master bath and ample storage. Easy to show, schedule your appointment to see it TODAY!
